## Hardware Target (Omnibus Profile)

- **Compute:** Raspberry Pi 5 16GB + Hailo-10H NPU
- **Transport:** NATS JetStream (local, 40MB memory cap)
- **Inference Tier 1:** Phi-3-mini / Moondream-2 on Hailo-10H (< 200ms)
- **Inference Tier 2:** Qwen2.5-7B via llama.cpp on CPU (< 2s)
- **Physical vessel:** Wibo 835 steel sloop

